## Stack (do not change without user approval)

Backend: FastAPI ¬∑ Beanie + MongoDB Atlas ¬∑ Qdrant ¬∑ Celery + Redis ¬∑ Docling ¬∑ EasyOCR ¬∑ BGE-M3 ¬∑ BGE reranker ¬∑ Qwen3 4B (Ollama) ¬∑ OpenAI-compatible API fallback
Frontend: React + TypeScript (Vite)
Config: `.env` + `config/*.yaml` ‚Äî ALL thresholds and top_k live here, never hardcoded

