## Layer Rules (enforce strictly)

| Path | Role |
|---|---|
| `backend/src/api/v1/endpoints/` | Thin handlers only ‚Äî no business logic |
| `backend/src/agentic/` | Bounded multi-step orchestration |
| `backend/src/inference/` | LLM orchestration, intent, confidence, response parsing |
| `backend/src/processing/` | Parsing, OCR, chunking, extraction, enrichment |
| `backend/src/rag/` | Embedding, Qdrant, retrieval, reranking, CRAG |
| `backend/src/guardrails/` | Refusal, claim verification, contradiction |
| `backend/src/schemas/` | Pydantic v2 schemas ‚Äî request / response / domain |
| `backend/src/models/` | Beanie documents (MongoDB) |
| `backend/src/tasks/` | All Celery async jobs |
| `config/*.yaml` | All thresholds, prompts, limits |

